snippet.title: Best VGM 824 - Ar Tonelico - Valkyrja
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 471 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SsFYXts6EeE

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Ar Tonelico (2007)
Valkyrja
Ken Nakagawa, Daisuke Achiwa & Akira Tsuchiya
